subject: p13031876
Findings: Portable AP chest radiograph was compared to prior study obtained the same day earlier. The recently introduced Dobbhoff tube tip is at the level of mid portion of the esophagus and should be further advanced. No changes in the appearance of the multifocal lung opacities and cardiomediastinal silhouette demonstrated.
